<A>__{high angle, at second story level. nancy looks directly across the street to a lighted, open window. its curtains, sucked out and waving in the night breeze, give the only motion to the deserted street. then someone pitches out of the dark at her. nancy gives a yelp then clamps her hand over her mouth as she recognizes glen, balanced precariously on the rose trellis outside her window.}
